                  <handDesc>
                  <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                  <seg type="rubrication">
                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢየሱስ፡</foreign>
                  </seg>
                  <desc>The word Jesus is rubricated</desc>
                  </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1"><locus target="#11r" facs="011">Fol. 11r</locus><desc>The Raising of Lazarus with caption <q>“How Lazarus rose.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#41r" facs="041">Fol. 41r</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1086StrikingHead">The Striking of the Head, ኵርዓተ፡ ርእሱ፡</ref> with caption <q>“How they struck the head of Our Lord.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#77v" facs="078">Fol. 77v</locus><desc>Jesus Teaching the Disciples with caption <q>“How he taught the disciples.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d4">
                    Decorative designs:
                    <locus target="#1r" facs="001">fols. 1r, </locus> (haräg);
                    <locus target="#22v #43v #62r #65v #77r" facs="023 044 062 066 077">22v, 43v, 62r, 65v, 77r</locus> (multiple full stops)
                    </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="a1">
                    <locus target="#18r" facs="018">Fol. 18r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Record of a provision of the will of the owner: “A curse on the [heir] who would sell this book; may he be condemned like Arias on the authority of Peter and Paul. Let [the heir] who cannot read it, give it to the [heir] who can read it.”
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <locus target="#17 #49 #53 #68 #76" facs="017 049 053 068 076">Fols. 17, 49, 53, 68, 76</locus>
                    <desc>
                    red yarn is sewn into the fore edge to mark content as navigation system
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <locus target="#1r #1v #2r #2v #3r #3v #4r" facs="001 002 003 004">Fols. 1r, 1v, 2r, 2v, 3r, 3v, 4r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    (etc.) words of text are written interlinearly
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e3">
                    <locus target="#3v #7r #10r #12r #13r" facs="004 007 010 012 013">Fols. 3v, 7r, 10r, 12r, 13r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    (etc.) lines of text are written interlinearly
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <locus target="#6r #53v" facs="006 054">Fols. 6r, 53v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    erasure markings are visible
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e5">
                    <locus target="#9v #10r #12r #15v #22v" facs="010 012 016 023">Fols. 9v, 10r, 12r, 15v, 22v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    (etc.) text has been removed
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                  </list>
                </additions>
                <bindingDesc>
